kind": "text", "text": ", q. v.) ―         -b3-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jaAw^uwA", "text_ar": "جَاوُوا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jamaAraY", "text_ar": "جَمَارَى", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and with tenween, [i. e., app.,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jamaArFA", "text_ar": "جَمَارًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", not, as might be thought at first sight,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jamaArFY", "text_ar": "جَمَارًى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", a form which MF disapproves, though it is said in the TA that his disapproval requires consideration,]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "They came all together,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "all of them."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K.)"}], "source_refs": ["K", "As", "TA"]}, {"entry_id": "n6279", "headword_ar": "جُمَّارٌ", "root": "jmr", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": "(S, A, Mgh, Msb, K) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jaAmuwrN", "text_ar": "جَامُورٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K) [each a coll. gen. n.] The"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "heart,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "pith,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "cerebrum,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the palm-tree,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, A, Msb, K, TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that is in the summit of its head, which part is cut off, and its outer portion is stripped off from the pith within it, which is a white substance, like a piece of the hump of a camel, large and soft: it is eaten with honey:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "from it come forth the fruit and the branches; and when it is cut off, the tree dies:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the spathe comes forth from it, amid the part whence two branches divide:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "head of the palmtree; a soft, white substance:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "from"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jam~ara", "text_ar": "جَمَّرَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "“ he collected together; ” for a similar reason termed"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "kavarN", "text_ar": "كَثَرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (Mgh:) n. un."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jum~aArapN", "text_ar": "جُمَّارَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (A, TA.) [See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qalobN", "text_ar": "قَلْبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".] You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lahu saAqN kaAljum~aArapi", "text_ar": "لَهُ سَاقٌ كَالجُمَّارَةِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He has a shank like a piece of the heart of the palm-tree."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Aljum~aAru fiY xalaAxilihin~a", "text_ar": "الجُمَّارُ فِى خَلَاخِلِهِنَّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Legs like the heart of the palm-tree are within their anklets"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (A.) Sakhr El-Hudhalee says, using a double trope, likening the fresh juicy stalks of the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "barodiY~", "text_ar": "بَرْدِىّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "to the pith of the palm-tree, and then applying this expression to the legs of a woman,"}, {"kind": "quote", "text": "A_i*aA EuTifato xalaAxuluhun~a gaS~abo\n                      \n                     \n                        bijum~aAraAti barodiY~K xidaAli"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "When their anklets are bent,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(for the anklet of the Arab woman is formed of a piece of silver, or other metal, which is bent round so that the two ends nearly meet,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "they are choked,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "entirely filled up, with plump legs like the pith of the papyrus"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (A, TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["S", "A", "Mgh", "Msb", "K", "TA"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}